channel.title: My Auto-Cache Downloader
channel.description: For some reason, i cant get my auto cache downloader to work. I am using the new one made by Google i believe and i did everything i was supposed to. Uploaded it to dropbox, changed the link in client and did the signlink thing too. Everytime i load my webclient, it starts up but then i get the error screen. i check my C:/ drive and it started to extract in the folder but then it just stopped. If anyone can help, please do
